{"tid":1561094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[借AC] 跳閘跳左成個禮拜~~究竟跳左D乜!!!","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T10:28:35.000Z","uid":223296,"like":43,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a4d7238071a567099ad3736f6b91b1ea2bbeb92d","tid":1561094,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"借ACC出，非本人<br />\n全世界人聽住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跳閘跳左成個禮拜可以話係失敗中既失敗<br />\n唔敢跳個D不在話下，跳既有D連口罩都唔戴返個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴左口罩都仲要鬼鬼鼠鼠，<br />\n跳左出黎仲要十條八條藍蛆追住你黎影，<br />\n一心諗住杯葛黨鐵，一蚊都唔比佢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到頭來仲要比黨鐵開張罰單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要嘔凸比黨鐵賺盡<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跳閘??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了!!</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">甘係咪等於要放過黨鐵??</span><br />\n當然唔係啦!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實唔搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有無人諗過全民一齊搭巴士</strong></span></span><br />\n每晚九點尻叫，每朝陸上交通壓力測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />塞爆佢老味<br />\n時間多串Ｄ仲可以等到有位先上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />坐膠晒Ｄ位唔比Ｄ廢老坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甘先做到真真正正一毫子都唔比黨鐵賺之餘仲可以阻住班港豬好鐘意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">各位手足，有無得諗？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f9b83f1d4d759dff4cdafd8dfde1f8f9eb72e8","tid":1561094,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"fcfb0257be04a9dc36f9d9f95d5a31094624b51d","tid":1561094,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d7238071a567099ad3736f6b91b1ea2bbeb92d","tid":1561094,"uid":223296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:51:13.000Z","msg":"借ACC出，非本人<br />\n全世界人聽住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跳閘跳左成個禮拜可以話係失敗中既失敗<br />\n唔敢跳個D不在話下，跳既有D連口罩都唔戴返個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />戴左口罩都仲要鬼鬼鼠鼠，<br />\n跳左出黎仲要十條八條藍蛆追住你黎影，<br />\n一心諗住杯葛黨鐵，一蚊都唔比佢賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到頭來仲要比黨鐵開張罰單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要嘔凸比黨鐵賺盡<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">跳閘??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"